OK! Magazine Special - The Amazing 90s, 2013
English | 84 pages | HQ PDF | 72.00 Mb

Ah, the 90s, worth looking back on ? if only to marvel at the giant cell phones! But the editors of OK! put together a special collector?s issue packed with so much more favorites from the decade that launched Julia Roberts, Brad Pitt and Titanic; pitted grunge against boy bands; and welcomed a wonder called the World Wide Web! With quizzes on the movies, music and TV shows that defined the times and a look back at 90s fashion. From the Fresh Prince to Friends to flannel, this is all you need to achieve 90s pop culture Nirvana!
